---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "ORV-Reader"
---

<style>
  .quote-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .quote-container::before,
  .quote-container::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border: 2px solid white;
  }
  .quote-container::before {
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    border-right: 0;
    border-bottom: 0;
  }
  .quote-container::after {
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    border-left: 0;
    border-top: 0;
  }

  @keyframes glowOnLoad {
    0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 0px transparent; }
    50% { text-shadow: 0 0 15px white; }
  }

  .made-by-glow {
    animation: glowOnLoad 3s ease-in-out;
  }
</style>

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-evenly w-full max-w-3xl shrink-0">
  
  <img src="/assets/images/banner.webp" 
       class="w-full max-w-125 h-auto" 
       alt="ORV Logo" />

  <div class="quote-container">
    <p class="font-mono uppercase md:text-lg text-sm text-white/90">
      “There are three ways to survive a apocalypse. I have forgotten some of them now, but one thing is certain: you, who are currently reading these words, will survive.”
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 w-full">
    {% set btnClass = "flex-1 min-w-[200px] max-w-[280px] inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold text-[0.95rem] no-underline transition-all duration-300 backdrop-brightness-75 hover:bg-white/5" %}
    
    <a href="./story/" class="{{ btnClass }}">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
